<taxonomicName id="91308B2C90E64CD76444034849F59054" class="Bivalvia" family="Veneridae" genus="Tapes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tapes marmorata" order="Venerida" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="marmorata">Tapes marmorata</taxonomicName>
Lamarck, leg. J. C. Melvill, NMW 1955.158: Thalassery (Tellicherry), Northern Kerala, 4 empty articulated shells, as 
<taxonomicName id="A0A0DE0B6E080BB202A640E13742AE29" authority="Römer, 1864" authorityName="Römer" authorityYear="1864" class="Bivalvia" family="Veneridae" genus="Hemitapes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemitapes marmorata" order="Venerida" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="marmorata">Hemitapes marmorata</taxonomicName>
